    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "M-27\nMIAMI TERMINAL OF PAN AMERICAN AIRWAYS\nPHOTO BY W. F. GERECKE\n6А-H1644",
      "THOMAS R. WEST, MIAMI, FLA.\nThousands of\npassengers and tons of International\nAir Mail and\nExpress\npass\nthru\nair terminal\neach year.\nThe great \"Clipper Ships\"\nwithin a few\nand\ndays travel of\n32\nbring\nMiami\ncountries of South\nCentral\nAmerica\nand the\nWest\nIndies.\nThis\nis the\nworld's largest International Airport.\nPOST CARD\nTHIS SPACE FOR ADDRESS ONLY\nPLACE\nONE CENT\nSTAMP\nHERE\n20221291515"
    ],
